00:12:21.260 --> 00:12:23.260
Uite, al nostru e mai roşu, e mai lung.

00:12:23.260 --> 00:12:26.260
Ne-au furat steagul! Ne-au furat steagul!"

00:12:26.260 --> 00:12:31.260
